            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-description field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>The Canterbury Recreation Complex is the ideal place to meet your recreational needs. The facility boasts a 25 metre five lane swimming pool with sauna, an NHL sized ice rink in the Brian Kilrea Arena and the Canterbury Community Centre. Our pool offers a wide selection of aquatic programs including public swims, aquafitness and swimming lessons.</p>
<p>Canterbury Recreation Complex offers a variety of programs for all ages. Through a partnership with the <a href="http://cca-acc.ca/">Canterbury Community Association</a>, children's and adult programs are also available to the Canterbury community. These programs include: an after school program, adult and senior fitness programs, as well as art, dance, martial arts and yoga programs for all ages.</p>
